text: Her sutelat wa landgemæru into B<../images/etail.gif>dintun.
& swa forð to mearðes <scage> & swa forð ofer þa blacelege to sproges forda.
Of sproges forda andlang þæs broces to gate brycge.
& of gate brycge into swompes næpe.
& of swompes hnæpe into sceddern þorn.
& of sceadder þorn ofer þæne mor into þam sur æppeltreo æt þære nearawan sætan.
& fram þære nearawan sætan in þæne holgan broc æt wulfgares more.
& swa forð andlanges þæs broces forð<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to þam stanian forda.
& of þam stanian forda andlang þæs sices<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to þam smæle æcels.
& swa forð andlangas þæs broces forð<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to hryxies mæne weig.
& þanone oð<../images/tbar.gif>hit cumð to godrices lea.
& of godrices lea to wulstanes forda.
& þanone oð<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð under þære blacan ecge to þære srtæte & ofer þa stræte.
